#include<iostream>
#include<cstdio>
using namespace std;

#define gc() getchar_unlocked()
static inline int fastio()
{
    int x=0;
    char c=gc();
    while(c<'0'||c>'9')
        c=gc();
     while(c>='0'&&c<='9')
     {
         x=(x<<1)+(x<<3)+c-'0';
         c=gc();
     }
     return x;
}

int main()
{
    int t,n,i,flag[101],x;
    t=fastio();
    while(t--)
    {
        n=fastio();
        for(i=1;i<=100;i++)
            flag[i]=0;
        for(i=1;i<=n;i++)
        {
            x=fastio();
            flag[x]++;
        }
        for(i=1;i<101;i++)
        {
            if(flag[i]==1){
                printf("%d\n",i);
                break;}
        }
    }
    return 0;
}
